Package: audyn
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Recommends: pipewire
Description: AES67 audio capture and archival engine
 Audyn is a professional-grade audio capture system for AES67/PTP
 networked audio streams with PipeWire fallback support.
 .
 Features:
  - AES67 RTP receiver with PTP/TAI timestamping
  - PipeWire fallback input for local audio capture
  - WAV and Opus/Ogg output formats
  - Rotter-compatible archive rotation and file naming
  - Lock-free frame pool and audio queue
  - Jitter buffer with PTP clock synchronization
  - systemd service integration
